mil.navy.nrl.cmf.sousa
Class SelectableSet

java.lang.Object
  mil.navy.nrl.cmf.sousa.SelectableSet
public class SelectableSet
extends Object

SelectableSet is a set of Selectable waiting to perform I/O operations together with the means to determine which of them is ready for I/O.

private Object _blocked
Semaphore for concurent I/O

_selectables

private HashMap _selectables
Tracks each Selectable and its Selectable.Handler by SignalType. The keys are SignalType. The values are Maps where the keys are Selectable and the values are Selectable.Handler.

_marks

private HashMap _marks
Tracks each Selectable and its desire for I/O state by SignalType. The keys are SignalType and the values are HashMap with Selectable as keys and Boolean as values. true indicates that the Selectable desires to perform the I/O indicated by the SignalType.

_notifications

private HashMap _notifications
Tracks each Selectablethat is ready for I/O by SignalType. The keys are SignalType and the values are List of Selectable.

_thread

private Thread _thread
The Thread under which select(long) is running.
